
Installation directions for NrrdIO.

Install using cmake.
Type "ccmake ." and "c" twice to configure.
Check that IJK_DIR is set to the main directory under which you want 
to install the library ITKNrrdIO.
(If not, modify the path for IJK_DIR.)
Press "g" to generate the Makefile and exit.
Type "cmake .".
Type "make" to create "libITKNrrdIO.a".
Type "make install" to install "libITKNrrdIO.a" in directory ${IJK_DIR}/lib.

